<!-- ============== PROFILE ================= -->
<div id="profile">

<img id='photo' src="img/photo.png" title="Thomas Debeauvais" alt="Photo of Thomas Debeauvais" />

<p>
My name is Thomas Debeauvais. I'm a PhD student in the Informatics department of <abbr title="University of California, Irvine">UCI</abbr>. My advisor is <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~lopes">Crista Lopes</a>. I plan to graduate sometime in 2015.

I study player behavior in games, with a particular interest on retention, real-money transactions, skill, and content consumption.

Have a look at my <a href="files/debeauvais_resume.pdf">resume</a>, <a class='goto-projects' href="#papers">research projects</a>, <a href="https://github.com/gentimouton">github page</a>, or drop me an email at: tdebeauv (then @uci.edu)
</p>

</div>


